<div id="Welcome">
    <h2>Welcome to Global Climate Vision</h2>
    <img src="~/img/Images/logo2cropped.jpg" alt="Organisation Logo" />
    <h3>Who are we</h3>
    <p>We welcome you to this organisation and present to you this newly created website where we can get involved with matters relating to climate change. We are a non-profit organisation that is trying to spread awareness about the effects of global warming and are encouraging others to take action along with us.</p>
    <p>We have a vision that one day global warming will no longer be an issue to our planet but getting will take a lot of effort and time. We need people like you that can help us towards our main goal and reduce the effects of climate change. And possibly eliminate global warming caused by humans all together. So, we are just a group people who have created this organisation to heal the planet and we are in need of assisstance.</p>
    <h3>What we do</h3>
    <p>We help people reduce their carbon footprints and spread awareness of climate change.</p>
    <p>We also participate in many activities such as planting trees so donating could really us in fighting for the environment.</p>
    <p>To donate, you will need to register to our website and then you are set up and have full access to features in this website.</p>
    <h3>How we can help</h3>
    <p>We will guide you on how you can make a difference in stopping global warming, no matter how a big or small change. We offer services in helping you change your lifestyle for the health of the environment which you will need an account to access. Make sure you stay tuned for challenges and prizes that you can win from helping us in fighting global warming. We also keep you up-to-date with news/information relating to climate change.</p>
